text: José Luis Aguirre (born 8 March 1967) is a Spanish rower. He competed in the men's coxless four event at the 1988 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1967 births Category:Living people Category:Spanish male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Spain Category:Rowers at the 1988 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
